en_7203215_0	COLOMBO (News 1st) – A special convention for the representatives of the SLFP chaired by President Maithripala Sirisena will be held today (December 04) at 2 p.m. at the Sugathadasa Indoor Stadium.
en_7203215_1	The convention is themed “Decision for the country” at which the President is expected to make a special statement.
en_7203215_2	Speaking to News 1st, the Secretary-General of the SLFP, Prof. Rohana Lakshman Piyadasa said this convention will cover several areas including the current political deadlock.
en_7203215_3	He added that Parliamentarians, provincial councilors and other representatives of the SLFP will be attending the event.
